Wellness with @jessicastone_co 💚 Jessica Stone is an intuitive guide and healer with a deep passion for empowering individuals to reconnect with their soul’s purpose.

Through her work as a Reiki practitioner, meditation guide, breathwork teacher, and brand consultant, she helps people navigate their personal and spiritual journeys with clarity and light. With over seven years of experience, Jessica has cultivated a successful business that includes speaking engagements, an educational platform, and collaborations with renowned brands. Read more about her journey and how she incorporates Juna into her daily routine on our blog, link in bio!
